statements: SELECT * FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE agent_id = 1;
SELECT agent_name, policy_type FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE policy_amount > 1000;
SELECT agent_id, policy_type, policy_amount FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE commission_rate < 0.05;
SELECT agent_id, agent_name, policy_type, policy_amount FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE policy_type = 'Life';
SELECT agent_id, agent_name, policy_type, policy_amount, commission_rate FROM InsuranceAgents ORDER BY agent_id DESC;
SELECT agent_id, agent_name, policy_type, policy_amount FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE commission_rate > 0.05 ORDER BY agent_name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT agent_name, policy_type, policy_amount FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE policy_amount > 1000 AND commission_rate < 0.1 ORDER BY policy_amount ASC, agent_name DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT agent_id, agent_name, policy_id, policy_type FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE policy_type LIKE '%health%' OR policy_type LIKE '%life%' ORDER BY agent_id ASC, policy_type DESC;
SELECT agent_name, SUM(commission_rate * policy_amount) AS total_commission FROM InsuranceAgents GROUP BY agent_name HAVING total_commission > 5000 ORDER BY total_commission DESC;
SELECT agent_id, agent_name, policy_type, policy_amount, commission_rate FROM InsuranceAgents WHERE agent_id IN (2, 5, 8) ORDER BY agent_id ASC, policy_amount DESC;

SELECT * FROM CommissionPayments WHERE payment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31'
